Package index

Fitting Models

The main function for specifying and fitting bivariate copula models with flexible marginal distributions.

fit_bivariate_copula()
Fit Bivariate Copula Model

Working with Results

S3 methods for inspecting fitted models, extracting posterior summaries, and obtaining point estimates.

print(<copula_fit>)
Print a copula_fit object
summary(<copula_fit>)
Summarize a copula_fit object
coef(<copula_fit>)
Extract point estimates from a copula_fit

Internals

Internal constructor and utilities. These are documented for transparency but are not intended for direct use.

copula_fit()
Create a copula_fit object
get_stan_model()
Get the compiled Stan model (compiles on first use, caches for reuse)
